      "id": "PopularPost244413",
      "post_content": "Throughout my fantasy career I have seen just about every sword  \nI have battled with and against frostmourne in my time with the Horde  \nI have read of Excalibur, Masamune, Hywelbane and Sanglamore  \nI have seen scimitars, broadswords and other weapons of war  \nI have played against war and peace, famine and feast  \nI have seen razors, daggers, dirks and the claws of the beast  \nI have even seen the horror of a certain jitte  \nBut there is one blade that really ruins my day  \nThat one frustrating blade is the blade of doom  \nVoid without substance but it cuts like steel   \nRemoval flying around, I am like \u201cfor real!?\u201d  \nI sac my 20 tokens with a doubling season down  \nEighty one one army deserving of its renown   \nI am pretty happy, gonna beat him with my zoo  \nBut something is wrong\u2026my friend taps for two  \nOne swamp\u2026two swamps I may have to bite him  \nI known what is coming and I must say it looks grim  \nDoom blade, doom blade, on my Kozilek  \nDoom blade, Doom blade, I\u2018m a crying wreck  \nI play mostly green and a bit of... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "Stinga",
