      "id": "PopularPost180813",
      "post_content": "Iconic black removal 5/5  \n  \nblack: destruction [doom blade](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=doom blade)  \nwhite: exile [path to exile](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=path to exile)  \nred: burn [lightning bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=lightning bolt)  \nblue: counter [counterspell](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=counterspell)  \ngreen: combat tricks (!?) [giant growth](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=giant growth)  \n  \nEDIT:  \n@TheMurderousKitten   \n  \nI totally agree on that point.   \nIt was more meant like its a classic black MECHANIC - i know that its not classic in the sense of \"old\".  \nThe examples i chose were the ones that (on my opinion) are the best/most commonly used nowadays for each mechanic/color. (although \"best\" is relative, i know - you get the idea)  \nThats the reason why there is [doom blade](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=doom blade) in ![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol) and [counterspell](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=counterspell) in ![Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=U&type=symbol) on my list.   \n  \nBut i agree that the wording \"classic\" is surely a little bit misleading - deleted it :)",
      "posted_by": "ChaosK",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost180813\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">Iconic black removal 5/5<br/><br/>black: destruction <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"doom blade\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=doom blade\">doom blade</a><br/>white: exile <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"path to exile\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=path to exile\">path to exile</a><br/>red: burn <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"lightning bolt\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=lightning bolt\">lightning bolt</a><br/>blue: counter <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"counterspell\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=counterspell\">counterspell</a><br/>green: combat tricks (!?) <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"giant growth\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=giant growth\">giant growth</a><br/><br/>EDIT:<br/>@TheMurderousKitten <br/><br/>I totally agree on that point. <br/>It was more meant like its a classic black MECHANIC - i know that its not classic in the sense of \"old\".<br/>The examples i chose were the ones that (on my opinion) are the best/most commonly used nowadays for each mechanic/color. (although \"best\" is relative, i know - you get the idea)<br/>Thats the reason why there is <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"doom blade\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=doom blade\">doom blade</a> in <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"counterspell\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=counterspell\">counterspell</a> in <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Blue\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=U&amp;type=symbol\"/> on my list. <br/><br/>But i agree that the wording \"classic\" is surely a little bit misleading - deleted it :)</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '180813'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy62829\">ChaosK</span>\r\n                                (7/22/2011 10:42:51 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n