      "id": "PopularPost235638",
      "post_content": "For being talked about so much, people rarely choose this thing in constructed. This thing its nice, but situationally annoying (That opponent who only has black creatures.) I cant wait for the black instant that says destroy target creature. ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol) would be fair i think.  \n  \n[Rend Flesh](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rend Flesh) and [Eyeblight's Ending](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Eyeblight's Ending) are as close as you can get for the same cmc. If you add other colors it gives you stuff like [Putrefy](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Putrefy), [Maelstrom pulse](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Maelstrom pulse), and of course [Vindicate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Vindicate). Would it really break the game to add destroy target creature to ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol) Instant, of course not. That card would be far worse then [Terminate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Terminate), if the colors are relevant of course. I think its about time they gave me a destroy spell thats not situationally annoying.",
      "posted_by": "TheWrathofShane",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost235638\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">For being talked about so much, people rarely choose this thing in constructed. This thing its nice, but situationally annoying (That opponent who only has black creatures.) I cant wait for the black instant that says destroy target creature. <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/> would be fair i think.<br/><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Rend Flesh\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rend Flesh\">Rend Flesh</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Eyeblight's Ending\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Eyeblight's Ending\">Eyeblight's Ending</a> are as close as you can get for the same cmc. If you add other colors it gives you stuff like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Putrefy\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Putrefy\">Putrefy</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Maelstrom pulse\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Maelstrom pulse\">Maelstrom pulse</a>, and of course <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Vindicate\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Vindicate\">Vindicate</a>. Would it really break the game to add destroy target creature to <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/> Instant, of course not. That card would be far worse then <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Terminate\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Terminate\">Terminate</a>, if the colors are relevant of course. I think its about time they gave me a destroy spell thats not situationally annoying.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '235638'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy34054\">TheWrathofShane</span>\r\n                                (4/1/2012 3:08:47 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClear